
#view,index,type
GET /twitter/_mapping/tweet

GET /_mapping/tweet(type)
GET /_all/_mapping/tweet(type)

#All
GET /_all/_mapping
GET /_mapping


PUT /{index}/_mapping/{type}
{ body }

example
PUT twitter/_mapping/user
{
  "properties": {
    "name": {
      "type": "text"
    }
  }
}

updating existing mappings
存在的字段不会更新,没有的字段才会生效.

